923
01:55:33,830 --> 01:55:35,200
我只需輕輕一推
{\fs10\b0}I need to only give it a push.{\r}

924
01:55:39,250 --> 01:55:40,540
羅馬隕落之後呢
{\fs10\b0}And after Rome falls?{\r}

925
01:55:42,830 --> 01:55:43,830
然後怎樣
{\fs10\b0}What then?{\r}

926
01:55:46,700 --> 01:55:48,000
你真是你父親的孩子
{\fs10\b0}You are your father's child.{\r}

927
01:55:50,950 --> 01:55:52,830
他對羅馬的夢想從來不是夢
{\fs10\b0}His dream of Rome was never a dream.{\r}

928
01:55:53,830 --> 01:55:55,120
那是虛構的
{\fs10\b0}It was a fiction.{\r}

929
01:55:56,410 --> 01:56:02,450
最好的復仇就是變得與傷害你的人不同
{\fs10\b0}The best revenge is to become unlike the one who did the injury.{\r}

930
01:56:02,910 --> 01:56:07,250
我讓自己變得與你父親不同
{\fs10\b0}I have made myself unlike your father.{\r}

931
01:56:08,160 --> 01:56:10,660
他談論夢想 我講述真相
{\fs10\b0}He spoke of dreams, I speak of truth,{\r}

932
01:56:11,160 --> 01:56:13,080
在我的羅馬中唯一的真相
{\fs10\b0}and the only truth in my Rome{\r}

933
01:56:14,830 --> 01:56:16,500
就是強者的法則
{\fs10\b0}is the law of the strongest.{\r}

934
01:56:18,830 --> 01:56:19,790
我曾被
{\fs10\b0}I was owned{\r}

935
01:56:20,830 --> 01:56:23,290
一個皇帝奴役
{\fs10\b0}by an emperor.{\r}

936
01:56:26,700 --> 01:56:28,370
現在我統治著一個帝國
{\fs10\b0}Now I control an empire.{\r}

937
01:56:30,200 --> 01:56:32,750
除了羅馬 哪裏能讓人做到這一點
{\fs10\b0}Where else but in Rome can a man do that?{\r}

938
01:56:39,000 --> 01:56:42,750
你認出你父親在我身上留下的印記了嗎
{\fs10\b0}Do you recognize your father's mark on me?{\r}

939
01:56:48,290 --> 01:56:48,830
如果你
{\fs10\b0}If there is anything,{\r}

940
01:56:50,330 --> 01:56:54,450
在最後時刻需要什麼
{\fs10\b0}you need in these last hours,{\r}

941
01:56:55,950 --> 01:56:56,660
我們會提供
{\fs10\b0}we will provide.{\r}

942
01:57:03,410 --> 01:57:05,830
你的死亡將為我登上王位掃清道路
{\fs10\b0}Your death will clear my path to the throne.{\r}

943
01:57:08,080 --> 01:57:10,330
明天將會有角鬥表演
{\fs10\b0}Tomorrow there will be games,{\r}

944
01:57:11,160 --> 01:57:13,830
在那裏我將勝出
{\fs10\b0}and at them I will prevail.{\r}

945
01:57:29,080 --> 01:57:29,290
羅比
{\fs10\b0}Robbie.{\r}

946
01:57:36,830 --> 01:57:38,750
你能在明早前把消息送到奧斯提亞嗎
{\fs10\b0}Can you get me the message to Osti by morning?{\r}

947
01:57:39,540 --> 01:57:40,290
奧斯提亞有什麼
{\fs10\b0}What is it, Osti?{\r}

948
01:57:41,120 --> 01:57:41,750
那裏有一支軍隊
{\fs10\b0}There is an army.{\r}

949
01:57:44,830 --> 01:57:46,620
我請求你冒險 我的朋友
{\fs10\b0}I'm asking you to risk yourself, my friend,{\r}

950
01:57:46,700 --> 01:57:48,120
為了更偉大的事業
{\fs10\b0}on the surface of something greater.{\r}

951
01:57:51,700 --> 01:57:52,500
騎馬去奧斯提亞
{\fs10\b0}Ride to Ostia.{\r}

952
01:57:54,330 --> 01:57:56,950
把這枚戒指交給達裏烏斯·塞克斯圖斯將軍 你聽好了嗎
{\fs10\b0}Take this ring to General Darius Sextus, are you listening?{\r}

953
01:57:58,620 --> 01:58:02,660
達裏烏斯·塞克斯圖斯會認出這是阿卡修斯的戒指
{\fs10\b0}Darius Sextus, you will know as a Cacius' ring.{\r}

954
01:58:06,830 --> 01:58:10,370
那麼 大人 我該說什麼
{\fs10\b0}And, uh, what shall I say, sir?{\r}

955
01:58:11,330 --> 01:58:12,750
把戒指帶給他
{\fs10\b0}Send me with this ring.{\r}

956
01:58:16,370 --> 01:58:17,830
我是盧修斯·費裏斯·奧勒留
{\fs10\b0}I am Lucius Ferris Aurelius.{\r}

957
01:58:20,250 --> 01:58:20,750
羅馬王子
{\fs10\b0}Prince of Rome.{\r}

958
01:58:22,620 --> 01:58:25,750
告訴他我正召集軍隊保衛新共和國
{\fs10\b0}Tell him I am summoning the army to the defense of a new republic.{\r}

959
01:58:34,830 --> 01:58:36,700
要我考驗你嗎 要
{\fs10\b0}Shall I test you? Yes.{\r}

960
01:58:36,950 --> 01:58:37,910
要我嗎 要
{\fs10\b0}Shall I? Yes.{\r}

961
01:58:45,540 --> 01:58:46,830
羅比 我需要你的鑰匙
{\fs10\b0}Robbie, I need your keys.{\r}

962
01:59:34,160 --> 01:59:34,370
去吧
{\fs10\b0}Go!{\r}

963
01:59:34,950 --> 01:59:35,540
給我回來
{\fs10\b0}Come back!{\r}

964
02:00:06,910 --> 02:00:07,750
誰給你的這個
{\fs10\b0}Who gave you this?{\r}

965
02:00:09,250 --> 02:00:10,370
羅塞裏利烏斯的盧修斯
{\fs10\b0}Lucius the Roserilius.{\r}

966
02:00:12,200 --> 02:00:13,250
羅馬的王子
{\fs10\b0}The Prince of Rome.{\r}

967
02:01:06,830 --> 02:01:08,500
大人 這是我的街頭禮物
{\fs10\b0}My street gift, sir.{\r}

968
02:01:11,870 --> 02:01:14,500
只要她還活著 你就永遠不得安寧
{\fs10\b0}Until she dies, you will never know peace.{\r}

969
02:01:16,830 --> 02:01:17,370
永遠
{\fs10\b0}Ever.{\r}

970
02:01:28,790 --> 02:01:31,450
拉夫堡的民眾 死亡會激起暴民
{\fs10\b0}The people of Loughborough, death will incite the mob.{\r}

971
02:01:31,660 --> 02:01:34,410
如果她死了 街上的民眾起義絞死她
{\fs10\b0}If she dies and the streets rise up and hang her,{\r}

972
02:01:34,500 --> 02:01:36,000
我要讓他們明白卡拉卡拉的想法
{\fs10\b0}I shall drill into them Caracalla's head,{\r}

973
02:01:36,080 --> 02:01:39,620
民眾會讚頌我 因為我的朋友是政治
{\fs10\b0}and the people shall acclaim me that my friend is politics.{\r}

974
02:01:42,120 --> 02:01:44,750
開始吧 好
{\fs10\b0}Shall we? Yes.{\r}

975
02:02:01,160 --> 02:02:02,540
今天將是你最後一戰 冠軍
{\fs10\b0}Today will be your last fight, champion.{\r}

976
02:02:04,000 --> 02:02:06,580
我們的主人已經賜予你
{\fs10\b0}And our master has bestowed on you{\r}

977
02:02:07,830 --> 02:02:09,750
象徵自由的木劍
{\fs10\b0}the wooden sword of freedom.{\r}

978
02:02:13,830 --> 02:02:15,500
但你必須先贏得它
{\fs10\b0}But you have to earn it first.{\r}

979
02:02:16,790 --> 02:02:18,830
今天 你要為你的母親而戰
{\fs10\b0}Today, you're going to defend your mother.{\r}

980
02:02:42,370 --> 02:02:44,700
好一招 這一劍 這還是一劍
{\fs10\b0}What a steal, a point, this is still a point.{\r}

981
02:03:12,200 --> 02:03:16,410
為我而戰
{\fs10\b0}Fight for me.{\r}

982
02:03:32,290 --> 02:03:35,830
以卡拉卡拉皇帝的指控為名
{\fs10\b0}In honor of the accusations of Emperor Caracalla,{\r}

983
02:03:38,830 --> 02:03:43,660
第一議員多洛斯和第二議員馬克羅諾斯
{\fs10\b0}First Council, Dolos, and Second Council, Macronos,{\r}

984
02:03:44,080 --> 02:03:48,750
作為她密謀反對帝國的懲罰
{\fs10\b0}and as punishment for her conspiracy against the Empire,{\r}

985
02:03:49,250 --> 02:03:53,330
由於她對皇帝御用拉比的誹謗
{\fs10\b0}for her caliphes against the Emperor's imperial rabbi,{\r}

986
02:03:53,750 --> 02:03:56,330
以及煽動軍事叛亂
{\fs10\b0}and for fomenting military mutiny,{\r}

987
02:03:56,410 --> 02:04:01,000
連同她的希望 女王將面臨神聖的審判
{\fs10\b0}along with her hope, the Queen will face divine justice{\r}

988
02:04:01,080 --> 02:04:04,410
死於禁衛軍之手
{\fs10\b0}at the hands of the Praetorian Guard.{\r}

989
02:04:30,330 --> 02:04:34,790
我不是將軍 但我們都是老兵
{\fs10\b0}I'm not a general, but we are old soldiers.{\r}

990
02:04:35,830 --> 02:04:42,580
直到現在 我們戰鬥的目的不過是
{\fs10\b0}And up until now, we have fought for nothing more{\r}

991
02:04:42,660 --> 02:04:44,200
為了多活一天
{\fs10\b0}than another day's survival.{\r}

992
02:04:45,450 --> 02:04:46,370
你要我們做什麼
{\fs10\b0}What will you have us do?{\r}

993
02:04:48,160 --> 02:04:50,120
如果你們不願參與這場戰鬥
{\fs10\b0}Well, you can return to yourselves if you do not wish{\r}

994
02:04:50,200 --> 02:04:51,250
可以選擇離開
{\fs10\b0}to fight this battle.{\r}

995
02:04:52,750 --> 02:04:59,370
或者 你們可以加入我 為超越這些牆壁的
{\fs10\b0}Or, you can join me and fight for a freedom{\r}

996
02:04:59,450 --> 02:05:00,620
自由而戰
{\fs10\b0}far beyond these walls.{\r}

997
02:05:01,620 --> 02:05:02,750
曾經有一個時代 榮譽意味著面對敵人
{\fs10\b0}There once was a time when honor met the enemy,{\r}

998
02:05:02,830 --> 02:05:05,870
曾經有一個時代 在羅馬榮譽意味著一切
{\fs10\b0}there once was a time when honor meant something in Rome.{\r}

999
02:05:07,830 --> 02:05:12,540
在這個羅馬 我不再相信這些還存在
{\fs10\b0}In this Rome, I no longer believe that exists.{\r}

1000
02:05:12,950 --> 02:05:15,290
我們必須找回榮譽
{\fs10\b0}We must find it.{\r}

1001
02:05:16,830 --> 02:05:18,200
且記住
{\fs10\b0}And know this,{\r}

1002
02:05:20,330 --> 02:05:23,250
有死亡的地方 便沒有我們
{\fs10\b0}where death is, we are not.{\r}

1003
02:05:26,450 --> 02:05:30,200
有我們的地方 便沒有死亡
{\fs10\b0}Where we are, death is not.{\r}

1004
02:05:32,830 --> 02:05:34,160
為何是我的劍
{\fs10\b0}Why my sword?{\r}

1005
02:05:37,620 --> 02:05:38,120
直取另一個
{\fs10\b0}Straight to another!{\r}

1006
02:06:08,830 --> 02:06:13,790
不要說皇帝不懂仁慈
{\fs10\b0}Let it not be said that the emperor is not merciful.{\r}

1007
02:06:14,830 --> 02:06:18,250
女王將獲准選擇一名
{\fs10\b0}The queen will be granted a single{\r}

1008
02:06:18,330 --> 02:06:23,250
角鬥士對抗禁衛軍之神
{\fs10\b0}gladiator to defend her against the praetorian god.{\r}

1009
02:06:33,790 --> 02:06:35,790
冠軍 哈達姆
{\fs10\b0}The champion, Hadam!{\r}

1010
02:07:56,290 --> 02:07:58,200
騎兵隊 立刻鎮壓這場騷亂
{\fs10\b0}Someone in the cavalry put this down at once.{\r}

1011
02:07:59,540 --> 02:08:01,700
這是戰爭 真正的戰爭
{\fs10\b0}This is the war, real war!{\r}

1012
02:08:07,410 --> 02:08:10,750
阿爾切斯的軍隊已逼近羅馬城外 大人
{\fs10\b0}The army of Arces is advancing just outside of Rome, sir.{\r}

1013
02:08:13,120 --> 02:08:14,120
我們還能打敗他們
{\fs10\b0}We can still out-fight them.{\r}

1014
02:08:14,450 --> 02:08:16,540
他們只有五千兵力 不會更多
{\fs10\b0}They have only 5,000 troops, no more.{\r}

1015
02:08:18,370 --> 02:08:19,080
我們有多少人
{\fs10\b0}How many are we?{\r}

1016
02:08:20,080 --> 02:08:21,410
六千 或許更多
{\fs10\b0}6,000, perhaps more.{\r}

1017
02:08:21,950 --> 02:08:22,950
騎兵去城門守住
{\fs10\b0}Ride to the gate and hold us.{\r}

1018
02:09:12,540 --> 02:09:15,450
快逃
{\fs10\b0}Go for the escape!{\r}

1019
02:09:19,540 --> 02:09:19,750
十八
{\fs10\b0}eighteen?{\r}

1020
02:09:57,500 --> 02:09:59,000
把球給我 我的孩子 回家去吧
{\fs10\b0}Give me the ball. Go home, my son.{\r}

1021
02:09:59,700 --> 02:10:00,290
你看到天空了嗎
{\fs10\b0}Will you see the sky?{\r}

1022
02:10:02,040 --> 02:10:02,250
老大
{\fs10\b0}Boss!{\r}

1023
02:11:32,040 --> 02:11:37,750
這野蠻人怎麼殺不死
{\fs10\b0}Will nothing kill this barbarian?{\r}

1024
02:11:38,290 --> 02:11:40,160
我名叫盧修斯·巴裏斯·奧勒留
{\fs10\b0}Name is Lucius Barris Aurelius.{\r}

1025
02:11:40,830 --> 02:11:43,040
成為皇帝不只靠血統
{\fs10\b0}A man did not become emperor by bloodline alone,{\r}

1026
02:11:43,120 --> 02:11:46,250
必須用武力奪取 用武力保住
{\fs10\b0}must be taken by force and kept by force.{\r}

1027
02:11:46,330 --> 02:11:47,370
你就是這樣的人嗎
{\fs10\b0}Are you such a man as this?{\r}

1028
02:11:47,700 --> 02:11:48,950
我不為權力而戰
{\fs10\b0}I don't fight for power.{\r}

1029
02:11:50,000 --> 02:11:53,500
我為解放羅馬而戰 讓它擺脫你這樣的人 回歸人民
{\fs10\b0}I fight to free Rome from men like you and to return it to them.{\r}

1030
02:11:53,870 --> 02:11:56,540
眾神親臨 羅馬重生
{\fs10\b0}The gods themselves, what Rome reborn,{\r}

1031
02:11:56,750 --> 02:11:58,950
他們派我來完成這個使命
{\fs10\b0}they sent me to fulfill that task.{\r}

1032
02:11:59,040 --> 02:12:03,620
你的骨頭呢 第二個來殺你的人
{\fs10\b0}And what of your bones, second here to kill you?{\r}

1033
02:12:03,910 --> 02:12:04,120
啊
{\fs10\b0}Ah!{\r}

1034
02:12:05,500 --> 02:12:07,080
是時候結束這一切了 巴卡拉
{\fs10\b0}It's time to end this, Baccarat!{\r}

1035
02:12:07,950 --> 02:12:08,620
啊
{\fs10\b0}D'ah!{\r}

1036
02:12:29,040 --> 02:12:30,120
住手
{\fs10\b0}Don't!{\r}

1037
02:13:05,790 --> 02:13:06,160
停下
{\fs10\b0}Stop!{\r}

1038
02:13:16,450 --> 02:13:16,700
列克預測
{\fs10\b0}Lec forecasts{\r}

1039
02:13:16,790 --> 02:13:17,000
直接
{\fs10\b0}Straight up.{\r}

1040
02:13:18,040 --> 02:13:18,540
我的孩子
{\fs10\b0}My son.{\r}

1041
02:14:52,040 --> 02:14:53,950
你們期待我的演說
{\fs10\b0}You look to me to speak.{\r}

1042
02:14:54,040 --> 02:15:00,330
我除了說我們都經歷了太多苦難外 不知該說什麼
{\fs10\b0}I know not what to say other than we have all known too much, Dad.{\r}

1043
02:15:01,870 --> 02:15:04,750
但不能再為暴政流血了
{\fs10\b0}But no more blood be spilled in the name of tyranny.{\r}

1044
02:15:09,200 --> 02:15:14,080
我的祖父馬庫斯·奧勒留談到過羅馬的夢想
{\fs10\b0}My grandfather Marcus Aurelius talked of the dream that would be wrong.{\r}

1045
02:15:15,700 --> 02:15:22,040
一個我的父親馬克西姆斯·德西姆斯·梅裏迪烏斯為之犧牲的夢想
{\fs10\b0}A dream that my father, Maximus Decimus Meridius, died for.{\r}

1046
02:15:24,830 --> 02:15:25,410
一個理想
{\fs10\b0}An ideal.{\r}

1047
02:15:28,910 --> 02:15:32,370
一座為眾人而建的城市 一處庇護需要幫助之人的避難所
{\fs10\b0}A city for the many and a refuge for those in need.{\r}

1048
02:15:33,200 --> 02:15:35,040
一個值得為之奮鬥的家園
{\fs10\b0}A home worth fighting for.{\r}

1049
02:15:36,790 --> 02:15:40,750
一個馬克西姆斯用畢生守護的家園
{\fs10\b0}A home that Maximus spent his life defending.{\r}

1050
02:15:43,450 --> 02:15:44,660
夢想已失
{\fs10\b0}A dream is lost.{\r}

1051
02:15:50,040 --> 02:15:52,040
但黎明將至
{\fs10\b0}A day awake.{\r}

1052
02:15:54,040 --> 02:15:56,540
讓我們共同建造這個夢想
{\fs10\b0}We build that dream together.{\r}

1053
02:16:08,700 --> 02:16:09,660
你們意下如何
{\fs10\b0}What say you?{\r}

1054
02:17:32,290 --> 02:17:32,450
娜拉
{\fs10\b0}Nala.{\r}

1055
02:18:20,410 --> 02:18:27,250
父親 告訴我該怎麼做
{\fs10\b0}Speak to me, father.{\r}

1056
02:18:27,250 --> 02:18:35,250
